description_data.value: ** RESERVED ** This candidate has been reserved by an organization or individual that will use it when announcing a new security problem. When the candidate has been publicized, the details for this candidate will be provided.

descriptions.value: In Network Adapter Service, there is a possible missing permission check. This could lead to local denial of service with no additional execution privileges needed
En Network Adapter Service, es posible que falte una verificación de permiso. Esto podría provocar una denegación de servicio local sin necesidad de privilegios de ejecución adicionales.
